424
00:32:43,130 --> 00:32:45,900
Fokus dan lihat wajahnya.

425
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:48,930
Jang Ha Na!

426
00:32:49,970 --> 00:32:52,550
- Kenapa?
- Lampunya jatuh!

427
